Package PIM

Interface Microservice

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
FunctionalMicroservice, InfrastructureMicroservice
public interface Microservice extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
A representation of the model object 'Microservice'.

The following features are supported:

  • Microservice Name
  • Container
  • Components
  • Interface
  • Dependencies
  • Generating PSM
